    },
    {
      "id": "kInKMhBp7kO8awEtUc2QG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14571.352241844,
      "y": 355.34163552828784,
      "width": 351.7551439170036,
      "height": 122.99829130140287,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1A",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1515783620,
      "version": 387,
      "versionNonce": 199070881,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779880605997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Core entities;\n    - Merchant (business)\n    - PaymentIntent\n    - Transaction \n        - many transaction to one payment",
      "fontSize": 19.67972660822446,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core entities;\n    - Merchant (business)\n    - PaymentIntent\n    - Transaction \n        - many transaction to one payment",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "P5mvcASFgdEY4PvRKQoZ5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 14577.045717437444,
      "y": 573.8605920391902,
      "width": 599.9162081694687,
      "height": 590.3917982467339,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1B",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1255518716,
      "version": 599,
      "versionNonce": 996432001,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779880605997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API:\n    - merchant should be able to make a payment\n    POST /api/v1/payment-intents  -> paymentIntentId\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        amountInCents,\n        currency,\n        description\n    }\n\n   - users should be able to pay via credit/debit card\n   POST /api/v1/payment-intents/{paymentIntentId}/transactions\n   Headers: JWT\n   body: {\n     type,\n     cardDetails\n   }  \n\n    - merchant should be able to view status updates for payment\n    GET /api/v1/payment-intents/{paymentIntentId} -> PaymentIntent\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 19.67972660822446,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API:\n    - merchant should be able to make a payment\n    POST /api/v1/payment-intents  -> paymentIntentId\n    Headers: JWT\n    body: {\n        amountInCents,\n        currency,\n        description\n    }\n\n   - users should be able to pay via credit/debit card\n   POST /api/v1/payment-intents/{paymentIntentId}/transactions\n   Headers: JWT\n   body: {\n     type,\n     cardDetails\n   }  \n\n    - merchant should be able to view status updates for payment\n    GET /api/v1/payment-intents/{paymentIntentId} -> PaymentIntent\n    Headers: JWT\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
