      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779880810654,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Is the person/merchant making the requests who they say they are?\n    ❌  X-API-KEY: {apiKey} - easy for hackers\n    ✅ Signature of whole request with signature = HMAC-SHA256 (private_key, request)\n    ",
      "fontSize": 22.289811540390343,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Is the person/merchant making the requests who they say they are?\n    ❌  X-API-KEY: {apiKey} - easy for hackers\n    ✅ Signature of whole request with signature = HMAC-SHA256 (private_key, request)\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
